comments: I took her for dual credit, and she was a wonderful woman. You MUST have the book, it is used on the final. This is honestly one of the easiest classes you can take. She\'s available to help all the time, which is good, because there are times when it seems like she forgets to teach something. Just remember to ask questions and read the material.
mS Hill is the absolute sweetest teacher she understands everyones situations and have a personal relationship with each student IF YU NEED HELP JUST ASK HER!!!
